1.First we need to create three folder and paste kafka downloaded file inside the these folder.
2.select one folder and go inside config folder and take service.properties and change some ---
broker.id=1 put the broker id quinik.

listeners=PLAINTEXT://:9092 to do listeners=PLAINTEXT://localhost:9092
log.dirs=/tmp/kafka-logs to do log.dirs=/tmp/kafka-logs-1
put the zookeeper localhost of these node..
zookeeper.connect=localhost:2181,localhost:2182,localhost:2183





3-bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties
4-bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --topic TopicOne --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1
5.bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties
6.bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties
7.bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --describe --topic TopicOne
8.echo dump | nc localhost 2181 |grep brokers
9.echo dump | nc localhost 2181
10.bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092,localhost:9093,localhost:9094 --create --topic TopicSecond --partitions 3 --replication-factor 3
11.bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092,localhost:9093,localhost:9094 --describe --topic TopicSecond 
